08:44.149 --> 08:47.819
- Oh, nice! Beau, get over here!
- Oh, dear-- No.

08:53.909 --> 08:55.536
Did Principal Pat call him as well?

08:55.536 --> 08:57.412
No, I put this call in.

08:57.412 --> 08:59.289
While Dusty here was riding the bench,

08:59.289 --> 09:02.960
Beau Kovac was the starting point guard
of the Deerfield Hooves

09:02.960 --> 09:05.337
when we went 3-7 our senior year.

09:05.337 --> 09:08.298
