it would've been 1-9 probably.

09:08.298 --> 09:11.760
Okay, I can't just have non-teachers
walking around the gym willy-nilly.

09:11.760 --> 09:14.012
That's all right.
No one needs to call me "Teach."

09:14.012 --> 09:16.265
- You boys can just call me "Coach."
- Great.

09:16.265 --> 09:17.516
Or Coach Sheriff.

09:17.516 --> 09:19.017
So we have three coaches now?

09:19.017 --> 09:23.856
Better to have three coaches
than one who's a cheater.

09:25.607 --> 09:26.733
This is insane.

09:28.735 --> 09:30.195
That's cold.

09:30.195 --> 09:33.198
That's very intense, Beau. I love it!

09:33.198 --> 09:35.826
This is how you go 3-7, fellas!

09:35.826 --> 09:38.495
All right, circle up, top of the key.
Let's get some stretching in.

09:38.495 --> 09:40.622
No, fine, don't listen to me.
I'm just your teacher.

09:40.622 --> 09:44.209
No, that's not true, D.
You're also a whistler, baby.

09:45.127 --> 09:46.378
Don't need it.

09:46.378 --> 09:51.300
Listen, if you don't mind, I'd like
to go friggin' nuts on these boys.

09:51.300 --> 09:53.218
Really test their mental strength.

09:53.218 --> 09:56.096
Yeah, I would definitely mind that.

09:56.096 --> 09:58.807
- Boys, look in my eyes.
- Just take off the hat and be normal.

09:58.807 --> 10:00.017
- We're a team.
- Good.

10:00.601 --> 10:01.435
I'm normal.

10:02.311 --> 10:05.230
