Mr. Johnson.

10:05.230 --> 10:08.984
Okay, this is a whole new line
of MORPHO-inspired merchandise,

10:08.984 --> 10:11.695
and I'm giving you the chance
to get in on the ground floor.

10:11.695 --> 10:14.698
Wow, I know I would.

10:14.698 --> 10:16.950
I mean, these are all just samples,

10:16.950 --> 10:21.580
