of these little MORPHO key chains.

10:21.580 --> 10:23.624
- They're so cute! Or--
- So cute!

10:23.624 --> 10:24.750
Are you kidding me?

10:24.750 --> 10:29.087
You could get your potential printed
on a bumper sticker?

10:29.087 --> 10:30.172
How fun is that?

10:30.172 --> 10:31.673
- Very fun. So fun.
- So fun.

10:31.673 --> 10:33.550
