12:25.370 --> 12:26.455
Bring it in.

12:28.957 --> 12:29.958
Circle up!

12:29.958 --> 12:31.251
What's up, Axel?

12:32.377 --> 12:33.587
How's the team this year?

12:34.379 --> 12:35.547
It's not good, Mr. Kovac.

12:35.547 --> 12:38.258
And to be honest,
it's really hard to focus.

12:38.258 --> 12:40.844
