is try to win some games for him.

12:53.815 --> 12:55.234
Take out the bad guys.

12:55.234 --> 12:57.402
Are there any bad guys on this team?

12:58.237 --> 12:59.571
Anyone you don't trust?

13:00.155 --> 13:01.823
- Like, in a game?
- Yeah.

13:01.823 --> 13:05.827
Anyone seem distracted by other things?

13:06.995 --> 13:11.917
