for my scooter?

15:10.953 --> 15:12.371
Do you know where the clay is?

15:12.996 --> 15:13.997
Over there.

15:14.665 --> 15:15.666
Cool.

15:16.708 --> 15:18.961
So, remember when I said
I didn't want to hang out with you

15:18.961 --> 15:21.421
