15:22.673 --> 15:23.924
I'm sorry that I said that.

15:24.591 --> 15:27.719
I'm not the best at, like,
speaking sometimes.

15:28.428 --> 15:32.683
And just so you know,
Megan's party was pretty dumb. And boring.

15:33.559 --> 15:38.397
